000891 1000-INITIALIZATION.

000892     CALL 'CKSETADR' USING BINARY1
000893          UBAUXHCB-AUX-HIST-DCB-ADDR
000894          AUX-HIST-DCB.

000896     MOVE LOW-VALUES TO AUX-HIST-DCB.

