000914 * GET CURRENT DATE
000915     ACCEPT WS-CURR-DATE FROM DATE.
000916     MOVE WS-CURR-MO  TO WS-CURR-CONV-MM.
000917     MOVE WS-CURR-DAY TO WS-CURR-CONV-DD.
000918     MOVE 20          TO WS-CURR-CONV-CC.
000919     MOVE WS-CURR-YEAR TO WS-CURR-CONV-YY.
000920 CBR1* CALL 'CKDCEXIN' USING WS-CURR-CONV-DATE
000921 CBR1*                    WS-INT-CURR-DATE.

